<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">I had a hard time at first until I realized the beginning of each chapter has a symbol for the character who narrates the chapter. Once you know which<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">I had a hard time at first until I realized the beginning of each chapter has a symbol for the character who narrates the chapter. Once you know which character is speaking you can understand, and, imho fall in love with Leo Gursky. I am so in love with this character and this book. Bought it to give to my friends as well. Just thinking, been awhile since I read it, maybe time to read it for the third time.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
