      <div class=" clearFloats bigBox"><div class="h2Container gradientHeaderContainer"><h2 class="brownBackground"><a href="/work/quotes/1882970-the-history-of-love">Quotes from The History of Love</a></h2></div><div class="bigBoxBody"><div class="bigBoxContent containerWithHeaderContent">
